: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<p><a href=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/liferay-portal-doc-4.0.0.zip?download\" _fcksavedurl=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/liferay-portal-doc-4.0.0.zip?download\">Liferay Portal 4.0.0 JavaDocs</a><br><br><a href=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/liferay-portal-src-4.0.0.zip?download\" _fcksavedurl=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/liferay-portal-src-4.0.0.zip?download\">Liferay Portal 4.0.0 Source</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/liferay-portal-sql-4.0.0.zip?download\" _fcksavedurl=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/liferay-portal-sql-4.0.0.zip?download\">Liferay Portal 4.0.0 SQL Scripts</a><br><br><a href=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/liferay-portal-sql-oracle-9-4.0.0.dmp?download\" _fcksavedurl=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/liferay-portal-sql-oracle-9-4.0.0.dmp?download\">Liferay Portal 4.0.0 SQL Oracle 9 Dump</a><br></p><p><a href=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/liferay-portal-sql-oracle-10-4.0.0.dmp?download\" _fcksavedurl=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/liferay-portal-sql-oracle-10-4.0.0.dmp?download\">Liferay Portal 4.0.0 SQL Oracle 10 Dump</a></p><p><a href=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/liferay-portal-client-4.0.0.zip?download\" _fcksavedurl=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/liferay-portal-client-4.0.0.zip?download\">Liferay Portal 4.0.0 Axis Client</a><br><a href=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/layouttpl-deployer-4.0.0.xml?download\" _fcksavedurl=\"http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/lportal/layouttpl-deployer-4.0.0.xml?download\">\n</a></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>]]></dynamic-content>\n    <dynamic-content language-id=\"es_ES\"><![CDATA[<div>Liferay Portal soporta un amplio abanico de servidores de aplicaciones y contenedores de portlets. Liferay Portal Enterprise requiere un servidor de aplicaciones con soporte completo de J2EE mientras 