ackground-color: rgb(255, 182, 193);\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Note:</span>\nLiferay is not responsible for the code or images contained in\ncommunity portlets. If the portlet contain bugs or other issues, please\ncontact the original authors.</div><br>]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n</root>', 'general', 'BASIC-TEXT', 'BASIC-TEXT', SPECIFIC_TIMESTAMP_20060606175400, TRUE, 'liferay.com.1', 'Joe Bloggs', FALSE);
